.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-PENDING" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-pending \- list channels not yet in normal operation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-pending
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns channels whose state is not
.B CHANNELD_NORMAL
or
.BR CLOSED .
Covers opening, closing, and force-closing transitions.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, state, to_us_msat, total_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-list (1),
.BR lightning-channel-balance (1)
